## Limitations
This report is based on available data and publications up to October 2023. Some sources may have been updated or revised since then. Additionally, while the report focuses on human-induced causes of climate change, it does not extensively cover natural factors that may also contribute to climate variability. The findings are based on the consensus of the scientific community, which may evolve with new research and data.

